    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1999058/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1999058-12.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1999058/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">吉檀阿珂</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-11-26"
      class="main-meta">2007-11-26 20:42:50</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1247730_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  续：（上阙为《全唐诗》评论）  ......只是那些关于桃花的记忆，带着某种天真欢快的意味，更象是一阙唐代的小令。  C　　　　 那时我们有为期一周的“农忙假”。大约在五月下旬，农家的孩子们要在这个时期帮助家里做些力所能及的活。而我无活可帮，只好整天搬着小桌子坐在廊下...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1247730/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1247730_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1247730_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



